<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('../partials/head', { title }) %></head>
<body class="page-home">
<%- include('../partials/header', { activePage }) %>

<main class="home-main">
  <section class="home-hero home-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container home-hero-inner">
      <div class="home-hero-copy">
        <h1>Building Zambia's <span class="home-accent">Entrepreneurship</span> Ecosystem</h1>
        <p class="home-lead">
          Connecting visionary leaders with strategic guidance and practical support to catalyze sustainable growth across the Zambian landscape.
        </p>
        <div class="home-hero-actions">
          <a href="/ecosystem" class="home-btn home-btn-primary">Explore Our Ecosystem</a>
          <a href="/partner" class="home-btn home-btn-outline">Partner With Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-hero-visual">
        <div class="home-photo home-photo-hero">
          <img
            class="home-hero-img"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC_hoHR4d5BJ2tvjmjJXngZXHzUSGvepMmLHLDocdce7qlz6q95-VOa1xEiRn73Pq52OhHcXoj2StS-YyZl8a1TUwtP5n7YIybMEwRPTeM7JEBvHoaqkbDmTjK0R5x5Zu6agJVcC2P57egcROz4-DDOQ4NLG0d8qt248epapQfv-9IT_MGR32Mb7NxDlUezPCMlal6kNjnX_It9UeJhapVC0DfwwwC6UF3klwGmVnMqUYcSDqHFVDueoUWulE6nGU3ImvzfluhEfqo"
            alt="Entrepreneurs collaborating in a modern co-working space in Lusaka, Zambia"
            width="448"
            height="448"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          >
        </div>
        <div class="home-glass-card home-glass-stat">
          <div class="home-glass-stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6h-6z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="home-glass-stat-label">Zambia-Focused</span>
            <strong class="home-glass-stat-value">Entrepreneurship support</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-mission">
    <div class="container home-mission-inner">
      <div class="home-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <blockquote class="home-mission-quote">
        "Promoting entrepreneurship in Zambia by bridging the gap between local innovation and global excellence through practical support and structural connectivity."
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-ecosystem">
    <div class="container home-ecosystem-inner">
      <span class="home-pill">How We Work</span>
      <h2>A Connected Ecosystem</h2>
      <p class="home-ecosystem-lead">
        Moovex acts as the central hub, weaving together diverse businesses across sectors to create a resilient economic fabric. We don't just advise; we integrate, ensuring that every venture contributes to and benefits from the collective strength of the Zambian market.
      </p>
      <div class="home-feature-list">
        <article class="home-feature">
          <div class="home-feature-icon home-feature-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3s-1.34-3-3-3-3 1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5C15 14.17 10.33 13 8 13zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Strategic Connectivity</h3>
            <p>Forging partnerships that expand market reach and resource sharing.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="home-feature">
          <div class="home-feature-icon home-feature-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 3L1 12h3v8h6v-6h2v6h6v-8h3L12 3zm0 2.8L17 12h-2v6h-2v-6H9.8L12 5.8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Institutional Support</h3>
            <p>Providing the governance and structural stability needed for scale.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-portfolio">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="home-section-title">Our Portfolio</h2>
      <div class="home-portfolio-grid">
        <article class="home-card">
          <div class="home-card-top">
            <div class="home-card-icon home-card-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6 3h12v2H6V3zm0 4h12l-1 10H7L6 7zm2 12h8v2H8v-2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="home-card-badge">Ecosystem Partner</span>
          </div>
          <span class="home-card-category">Logistics &amp; Supply Chain</span>
          <h3>Chomaya</h3>
          <p class="home-card-desc">Microfuel and fuel-management solutions for PSV drivers, taxis, buses, and transport operators.</p>
          <div class="home-card-tags">
            <span>#Microfuel</span>
            <span>#FuelManagement</span>
            <span>#PSVSupport</span>
          </div>
          <div class="home-card-impact">
            <span class="home-card-impact-label">Impact Area</span>
            <strong>Transport &amp; Fuel Support</strong>
          </div>
          <a href="/portfolio#chomaya" class="home-btn home-btn-card">Learn More <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="home-card">
          <div class="home-card-top">
            <div class="home-photo home-photo-thumb" role="img" aria-label="GetPro team">
              <div class="home-photo-scene home-photo-scene-getpro">
                <span class="home-scene-headset"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <span class="home-card-badge">Ecosystem Partner</span>
          </div>
          <span class="home-card-category">Professional Services</span>
          <h3>GetPro</h3>
          <p class="home-card-desc">A call center and digital agency helping organizations improve customer service, work processes, websites, apps, and social media presence.</p>
          <div class="home-card-tags">
            <span>#DigitalAgency</span>
            <span>#ITSystems</span>
            <span>#CustomerSupport</span>
          </div>
          <div class="home-card-impact">
            <span class="home-card-impact-label">Impact Area</span>
            <strong>Digital Agency &amp; IT Systems</strong>
          </div>
          <a href="/portfolio#getpro" class="home-btn home-btn-card">Learn More <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="home-card">
          <div class="home-card-top">
            <div class="home-card-icon home-card-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 10v10h16V10H4zm2 2h12v6H6v-6zm2-6h8v2H8V6zm2-4h4v2h-4V2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="home-card-badge">Ecosystem Partner</span>
          </div>
          <span class="home-card-category">Infrastructure &amp; Tech</span>
          <h3>Facha</h3>
          <p class="home-card-desc">Stationery, internet café, wholesale drinks, and e-banking services for Airtel, MTN, Zamtel, Zanaco, FNB, and Indo-Zambia Bank.</p>
          <div class="home-card-tags">
            <span>#Ebanking</span>
            <span>#Wholesale</span>
            <span>#InternetCafe</span>
          </div>
          <div class="home-card-impact">
            <span class="home-card-impact-label">Impact Area</span>
            <strong>Ebanking &amp; Wholesale</strong>
          </div>
          <a href="/portfolio#facha" class="home-btn home-btn-card">Learn More <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="home-card">
          <div class="home-card-top">
            <div class="home-card-icon home-card-icon-teal" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 7V3H2v18h20V7H12zm-2 12H4v-2h6v2zm0-4H4v-2h6v2zm0-4H4V9h6v2zm8 8h-6v-2h6v2zm0-4h-6v-2h6v2zm0-4h-6V9h6v2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="home-card-badge">Ecosystem Partner</span>
          </div>
          <span class="home-card-category">Data Analytics</span>
          <h3>Netra</h3>
          <p class="home-card-desc">Commercial property management for shopping complexes, helping improve operations, tenant performance, customer traffic, and revenue.</p>
          <div class="home-card-tags">
            <span>#RevenueStreams</span>
            <span>#BusinessDevelopment</span>
            <span>#PropertyManagement</span>
          </div>
          <div class="home-card-impact">
            <span class="home-card-impact-label">Impact Area</span>
            <strong>Revenue Channels Development</strong>
          </div>
          <a href="/portfolio#netra" class="home-btn home-btn-card">Learn More <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-impact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="home-section-title home-section-title-light">Impact in Zambia</h2>
      <div class="home-impact-grid">
        <div class="home-impact-stat">
          <strong>Entrepreneurship</strong>
          <span>Support</span>
        </div>
        <div class="home-impact-stat">
          <strong>Growing</strong>
          <span>Portfolio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="home-impact-stat">
          <strong>Multiple</strong>
          <span>Business sectors</span>
        </div>
        <div class="home-impact-stat">
          <strong>Future</strong>
          <span>Impact reporting</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="home-cta-card home-soft-shadow">
        <div class="home-cta-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2>Support Practical Entrepreneurship in Zambia</h2>
        <p>
          Join us in building a sustainable future. Whether as a partner or a curious innovator, your journey with Moovex starts here.
        </p>
        <div class="home-cta-actions">
          <a href="/partner" class="home-btn home-btn-primary">Partner With Us</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="home-btn home-btn-outline">Contact Our Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
